11#ifndef LOGGING_RTC_EVENT_LOG_EVENTS_RTC_EVENT_ALR_STATE_H_
12#define LOGGING_RTC_EVENT_LOG_EVENTS_RTC_EVENT_ALR_STATE_H_
13
14#include <memory>
15
16#include "api/rtc_event_log/rtc_event.h"
17
18namespace webrtc {
19
20class RtcEventAlrState final : public RtcEvent {
21 public:
22 static constexpr Type kType = Type::AlrStateEvent;
23
24 explicit RtcEventAlrState(bool in_alr);
25 ~RtcEventAlrState() override;
26
27 Type GetType() const override { return kType; }
28 bool IsConfigEvent() const override { return false; }
29
30 std::unique_ptr<RtcEventAlrState> Copy() const;
31
32 bool in_alr() const { return in_alr_; }
33
34 private:
35 RtcEventAlrState(const RtcEventAlrState& other);
36
37 const bool in_alr_;
38};
39
40struct LoggedAlrStateEvent {
41 LoggedAlrStateEvent() = default;
42 LoggedAlrStateEvent(int64_t timestamp_us, bool in_alr)
43 : timestamp_us(timestamp_us), in_alr(in_alr) {}
44
45 int64_t log_time_us() const { return timestamp_us; }
46 int64_t log_time_ms() const { return timestamp_us / 1000; }
47
48 int64_t timestamp_us;
49 bool in_alr;
50};
51
52} // namespace webrtc
53#endif // LOGGING_RTC_EVENT_LOG_EVENTS_RTC_EVENT_ALR_STATE_H_
